     break long labels.
   - Added `.help-step > div { min-width: 0; flex: 1 1 auto; }` so the
     inner text column can shrink too.
   - `.help-step small`: smaller (0.72rem) and in a calmer grey.

Result: the pipeline always fits within the content pane — it wraps to
a second row on narrow widths but never scrolls sideways.

